cdata.name: StarKST
cdata.desc:
StarKST is a payment gateway system where users canmake safe and fast payments around the globe. The platform is developed using blockchain technology. The StarKST project offers to its users an exchange, a StarKST wallet to store, receive/send KST and finally, the StarKST website allocates the payment gateway.

The KST token use a private blockchain to improve the safety and quickness of the payments.
